#: ../../advanced/faq.md:1
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "常见问题（FAQ）"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:3
msgid "Common questions and their answers."
msgstr "常见问题与解答。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:7
msgid "General Questions"
msgstr "基本问题"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:9
msgid "What is ChatSpatial?"
msgstr "什么是 ChatSpatial？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:11
msgid ""
"ChatSpatial is an LLM agent for spatial transcriptomics analysis via MCP. It "
"integrates 60+ methods from Python and R ecosystems into a unified "
"conversational interface."
msgstr ""
"ChatSpatial 是一个通过 MCP 进行空间转录组分析的 LLM 智能体。它将 Python 与 R 生态中的 60+ 种方法整合为统一的对话式接口。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:13
msgid "What is MCP?"
msgstr "什么是 MCP？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:15
msgid ""
"MCP (Model Context Protocol) is an open standard that enables secure "
"connections between AI applications and external tools. ChatSpatial uses MCP "
"to allow LLMs like Claude to perform spatial analysis through natural "
"language."
msgstr ""
"MCP（Model Context Protocol）是一项开放标准，用于在 AI 应用与外部工具之间建立安全连接。ChatSpatial 使用 MCP，让 Claude 等 LLM 可以通过自然语言执行空间分析。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:17
msgid "What data formats does ChatSpatial support?"
msgstr "ChatSpatial 支持哪些数据格式？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:19
msgid "H5AD (AnnData format)"
msgstr "H5AD（AnnData 格式）"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:20
msgid "10X Visium spatial folders"
msgstr "10X Visium 空间数据文件夹"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:21
msgid "H5 files from 10X Genomics"
msgstr "10X Genomics 的 H5 文件"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:22
msgid "MTX matrix files"
msgstr "MTX 矩阵文件"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:23
msgid "Slide-seq, MERFISH, and other spatial formats"
msgstr "Slide-seq、MERFISH 以及其他空间数据格式"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:25
msgid "Do I need programming experience?"
msgstr "需要编程经验吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:27
msgid ""
"No! ChatSpatial is designed for natural language conversation. However, "
"understanding basic spatial transcriptomics concepts is helpful."
msgstr "不需要！ChatSpatial 旨在通过自然语言对话使用。不过，了解一些基础的空间转录组概念会更有帮助。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:31
msgid "Installation and Setup"
msgstr "安装与设置"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:33
msgid "What Python version do I need?"
msgstr "需要什么版本的 Python？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:35
msgid "Python 3.11 or higher (3.12 recommended, 3.13 supported)."
msgstr "Python 3.11 或更高版本（推荐 3.12，支持 3.13）。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:37
msgid "Should I use a virtual environment?"
msgstr "应该使用虚拟环境吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:39
msgid ""
"Yes, strongly recommended! Virtual environments prevent dependency conflicts."
msgstr "是的，强烈推荐！虚拟环境可以避免依赖冲突。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:41
msgid "How do I configure ChatSpatial?"
msgstr "如何配置 ChatSpatial？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:43
msgid ""
"See our [Configuration Guide](configuration.md) for MCP client setup "
"instructions."
msgstr "请参阅[配置指南](configuration.md)获取 MCP 客户端设置说明。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:45
msgid "Can I use ChatSpatial without Claude?"
msgstr "不用 Claude 也能用 ChatSpatial 吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:47
msgid "Yes! ChatSpatial works with any MCP-compatible client."
msgstr "可以！ChatSpatial 适用于任何兼容 MCP 的客户端。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:51
