#: ../../advanced/faq.md:78
msgid "Why does my analysis take so long?"
msgstr "为什么分析会这么慢？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:80
msgid "Large datasets and complex methods can be time-consuming. Tips:"
msgstr "大数据集与复杂方法会更耗时。建议："

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:81
msgid "Use GPU acceleration when available (Cell2location, scVI)"
msgstr "可用时使用 GPU 加速（Cell2location、scVI）"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:82
msgid "Reduce dataset size for initial testing"
msgstr "初次测试时先缩小数据规模"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:83
msgid "Use faster methods for exploratory analysis"
msgstr "探索阶段优先使用更快的方法"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:84
msgid "Check system resources (RAM, CPU)"
msgstr "检查系统资源（RAM、CPU）"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:86
msgid "How much memory do I need?"
msgstr "需要多少内存？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:88
msgid "Depends on dataset size:"
msgstr "取决于数据集大小："

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:89
msgid "Small (<5000 cells): 8GB RAM sufficient"
msgstr "小型（<5000 cells）：8GB 内存即可"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:90
msgid "Medium (5000-50000 cells): 16GB RAM recommended"
msgstr "中型（5000–50000 cells）：建议 16GB 内存"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:91
msgid "Large (>50000 cells): 32GB+ RAM needed"
msgstr "大型（>50000 cells）：需要 32GB+ 内存"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:95
msgid "Advanced Topics"
msgstr "高级话题"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:97
msgid "Can I use ChatSpatial in research publications?"
msgstr "可以在科研论文中使用 ChatSpatial 吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:99
msgid ""
"Yes! ChatSpatial is open-source under MIT license. Please cite our paper if "
"you use it in published research."
msgstr "可以！ChatSpatial 在 MIT 许可证下开源。如果你在发表研究中使用，请引用我们的论文。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:101
msgid "How do I contribute?"
msgstr "如何参与贡献？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:103
msgid ""
"See our [Contributing Guide](https://github.com/cafferychen777/ChatSpatial/"
"blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)."
msgstr "请参阅[贡献指南](https://github.com/cafferychen777/ChatSpatial/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:105
msgid "Can I add my own analysis methods?"
msgstr "可以添加自己的分析方法吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:107
msgid ""
"Yes! ChatSpatial's modular architecture makes it easy to add new tools. See "
"developer documentation."
msgstr "可以！ChatSpatial 的模块化架构便于添加新工具。请参阅开发者文档。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:109
msgid "Is GPU acceleration supported?"
msgstr "支持 GPU 加速吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:111
msgid ""
"Yes, for many methods including Cell2location, scANVI, STAGATE, and VeloVI. "
"Set `use_gpu=True` in parameters to enable."
msgstr "支持，许多方法（Cell2location、scANVI、STAGATE、VeloVI 等）都可以。将参数中的 `use_gpu=True` 即可启用。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:113
msgid ""
"See [Methods Reference](methods-reference.md) for the full list of GPU-"
"accelerated methods."
msgstr "详见[方法参考](methods-reference.md)中的 GPU 加速方法列表。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:117
msgid "Data and Privacy"
msgstr "数据与隐私"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:119
msgid "Is my data sent to external servers?"
msgstr "我的数据会发送到外部服务器吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:121
msgid ""
"No. ChatSpatial runs locally. Your data never leaves your computer. Only "
"natural language commands are sent to the LLM for interpretation."
msgstr "不会。ChatSpatial 在本地运行，你的数据不会离开你的电脑。只有自然语言指令会发送给 LLM 用于解析。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:123
msgid "Can I use ChatSpatial offline?"
msgstr "可以离线使用 ChatSpatial 吗？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:125
msgid ""
"Analysis tools work offline, but you need internet to communicate with the "
"LLM (Claude) for command interpretation."
msgstr "分析工具可离线运行，但要与 LLM（Claude）通信解析指令仍需要联网。"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:127
msgid "How is my data stored?"
msgstr "数据如何存储？"

#: ../../advanced/faq.md:129
msgid ""
"Data is stored in standard H5AD format. You control save locations through "
"the `CHATSPATIAL_DATA_DIR` environment variable."
msgstr "数据以标准 H5AD 格式存储。你可以通过 `CHATSPATIAL_DATA_DIR` 环境变量控制保存位置。"

